      <p>Version du graphique : <strong>{{ .Chart.Version }}</strong></p>
    </body>
    </html>

--

5. templates/deployment.yaml

apiVersion: apps/v1
kind: Deployment
metadata:
  name: {{ include « broapp.fullname » . }}
  labels:
    {{- include « broapp.labels » . | nindent 4 }}
spec:
  replicas: {{ .Values.replicaCount }}
  selector:
    matchLabels:
      app: {{ include « broapp.name » . }}
  template:
    metadata:
      labels:
        app: {{ include « broapp.name » . }}
    spec:
      containers:
      - name: broapp
        image: « {{ .Values.image.repository }}:{{ .Values.image.tag }} »
        imagePullPolicy: {{ .Values.image.pullPolicy }}
        ports:
        - name: http
          containerPort: 80
        resources:
          {{- toYaml .Values.resources | nindent 10 }}
        volumeMounts:
        - name: html
          mountPath: /usr/share/nginx/html
        livenessProbe:
          {{- toYaml .Values.livenessProbe | nindent 10 }}
        readinessProbe :
          {{- toYaml .Values.readinessProbe | nindent 10 }}
      volumes :
      - nom : html
        configMap :
          nom : {{ include « broapp.fullname » . }}-html

--

6. templates/service.yaml et ingress.yaml + NOTES.txt

=========================

Selesaikan Helm Chart "broapp"
Aku sudah buatkan file-file yang kurang supaya chart-nya bisa langsung dijalankan.

Tambahkan / Update File Berikut:
1. Update templates/_helpers.tpl (Ganti semuanya dengan ini)
YAML

{{- define "broapp.name" -}}
{{- default .Chart.Name .Values.nameOverride | trunc 63 | trimSuffix "-" }}
{{- end }}

{{- define "broapp.fullname" -}}
{{- if .Values.fullnameOverride }}
{{- .Values.fullnameOverride | trunc 63 | trimSuffix "-" }}
{{- else }}
{{- $name := default .Chart.Name .Values.nameOverride }}
{{- if contains $name .Release.Name }}
{{- .Release.Name | trunc 63 | trimSuffix "-" }}
{{- else }}
{{- printf "%s-%s" .Release.Name $name | trunc 63 | trimSuffix "-" }}
{{- end }}
{{- end }}
{{- end }}

{{- define "broapp.labels" -}}
helm.sh/chart: {{ include "broapp.chart" . }}
{{ include "broapp.selectorLabels" . }}
app.kubernetes.io/managed-by: {{ .Release.Service }}
{{- end }}

{{- define "broapp.selectorLabels" -}}
app.kubernetes.io/name: {{ include "broapp.name" . }}
app.kubernetes.io/instance: {{ .Release.Name }}
{{- end }}

{{- define "broapp.chart" -}}
{{- printf "%s-%s" .Chart.Name .Chart.Version | replace "+" "_" | trunc 63 | trimSuffix "-" }}
{{- end }}
2. Buat templates/service.yaml
YAML

apiVersion: v1
kind: Service
metadata:
  name: {{ include "broapp.fullname" . }}
  labels:
    {{- include "broapp.labels" . | nindent 4 }}
spec:
  type: {{ .Values.service.type }}
  ports:
    - port: {{ .Values.service.port }}
      targetPort: http
      protocol: TCP
      name: http
  selector:
    {{- include "broapp.selectorLabels" . | nindent 4 }}
3. Buat templates/ingress.yaml
YAML

{{- if .Values.ingress.enabled -}}
apiVersion: networking.k8s.io/v1
kind: Ingress
metadata:
  name: {{ include "broapp.fullname" . }}
  labels:
    {{- include "broapp.labels" . | nindent 4 }}
  annotations:
    nginx.ingress.kubernetes.io/rewrite-target: /
spec:
  ingressClassName: {{ .Values.ingress.className }}
  rules:
  - host: {{ .Values.ingress.host }}
    http:
      paths:
      - path: /
        pathType: Prefix
        backend:
          service:
            name: {{ include "broapp.fullname" . }}
            port:
              name: http
{{- end }}
4. Buat templates/NOTES.txt
YAML

Thank you for installing {{ .Chart.Name }} version {{ .Chart.Version }} !

**BroApp** has been deployed successfully! 🚀

{{- if .Values.ingress.enabled }}
You can access the application at:

    http://{{ .Values.ingress.host }}

{{- else }}
You can access via port-forward:

    kubectl port-forward svc/{{ include "broapp.fullname" . }} 8080:80
    Then open browser: http://localhost:8080
{{- end }}

Command untuk melihat status:
    helm status {{ .Release.Name }}
    kubectl get all -l app={{ include "broapp.name" . }}

le façon de tester le Chart :

une fois le fichier est marché, fait running ces commands :

# 1. Validation chart (c'est très important)
helm lint .

# 2. Install chart
helm install bro-test . --namespace bro-test --create-namespace

# 3. Lihat hasilnya
kubectl get all -n bro-test
helm list -n bro-test

--

une fois tous ça marche , essayez upgrade aussi:

helm upgrade bro-test . --namespace bro-test --set replicaCount=3

